{{!-- Tag marquee — the strip along the bottom of the hero.

     Tags carry their own icon when one is set: Ghost gives every tag a
     feature_image, so a tag with an image shows it; the rest fall back to a
     "#". That's the "icon if the tag has an icon" rule, and it needs no
     mapping table that would rot the moment a tag is renamed.

     filter="visibility:public" is load-bearing. {{#get}} applies `limit` to ALL
     tags and {{#foreach}} then silently drops internal #hash ones — which have
     the biggest post counts (#lesson, #course, #video…). Unfiltered, limit=14
     fetched 14 and rendered a handful. Filtering in the query means what we ask
     for is what we show.
     Don't add count.posts:>0 — NQL can't filter on that aggregate and the whole
     query silently returns nothing.

     The loop is written out twice on purpose: an {{#*inline}} partial declared
     inside this async {{#get}} breaks its own registration and the rail renders
     nothing at all. Copy #2 is aria-hidden AND tabindex="-1" so the tags aren't
     announced or tab-stopped twice. --}}
{{#get "tags" filter="visibility:public" limit="14" include="count.posts" order="count.posts desc" as |topics|}}
{{#if topics}}
<nav class="hx-strip hx-strip-reverse hx-strip-roomy" id="topics" aria-label="Topics">
	<span class="hx-strip-lead">
		<span class="hx-strip-lead-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
		Open to GTM Engineer role
	</span>
	<div class="group/strip hx-strip-view fade-mask-x">
		<div class="hx-strip-track group-hover/strip:[animation-play-state:paused]">

			<div class="hx-strip-group">
				{{#foreach topics}}
				<a href="{{url}}" class="hx-chip">
					{{#if feature_image}}
						<img src="{{img_url feature_image size="100"}}" width="20" height="20" alt="" loading="lazy" class="hx-chip-img" />
					{{else}}
						<span class="hx-chip-hash" aria-hidden="true">#</span>
					{{/if}}
					<span class="hx-chip-name">{{name}}</span>
					<span class="hx-chip-n">{{count.posts}}</span>
				</a>
				<span class="hx-chip-star" aria-hidden="true">✳</span>
				{{/foreach}}
			</div>

			<div class="hx-strip-group" aria-hidden="true">
				{{#foreach topics}}
				<a href="{{url}}" class="hx-chip" tabindex="-1">
					{{#if feature_image}}
						<img src="{{img_url feature_image size="100"}}" width="20" height="20" alt="" loading="lazy" class="hx-chip-img" />
					{{else}}
						<span class="hx-chip-hash">#</span>
					{{/if}}
					<span class="hx-chip-name">{{name}}</span>
					<span class="hx-chip-n">{{count.posts}}</span>
				</a>
				<span class="hx-chip-star">✳</span>
				{{/foreach}}
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<a href="{{@site.url}}/tags/" class="hx-strip-all">View all tags {{> "icons/arrow-right" class="h-3 w-3"}}</a>
</nav>
{{/if}}
{{/get}}
